  Locus:
    Page: 364
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Pessimism
---
Pessimists are second-rate people. They do not believe in life. Pessimism
is just an excuse for their cowardice. All they want is to drag you down
and appease their own feelings of mediocrity and fear.
